'''cerebellum'''  (''plural:'' '''[[cerebellums]]''' or '''[[cerebella]]''')

# {{anatomy}}: Part of the [[hindbrain]] in [[vertebrate]]s.  In [[human]]s it lies between the [[brainstem]] and the [[cerebrum]].  It plays an important role in sensory perception, motor output, balance and posture.

